                          "is a number which may be followed by an optional "
                          "'w', 'd', 'h', or 'm' (meaning weeks, days, hours, "
                          "minutes) and default to minutes.  METH is a string "
                          "'popup', 'email', or 'sms' and defaults to popup.")
